Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.07,0:00:16.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讨厌 不是那样的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.33,0:00:20.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的啦 你真的是胸部变大了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.54,0:00:22.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好恶心啊 不过...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.46,0:00:26.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去死......
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.59,0:00:28.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别留下你们劣性的基因
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.63,0:00:30.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发春的淫兽
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.63,0:00:32.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去死去死
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.28,0:00:34.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个是迷唇姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.28,0:00:34.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fs27}注释：口袋妖怪的一种
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.87,0:00:38.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不是 女人真的是笨啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.32,0:00:42.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是很像啊 嘴唇那么厚
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.62,0:00:43.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是这个理由的话
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.85,0:00:46.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,珠算学校的老爷爷也是迷唇姐了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.69,0:00:50.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是啊 仁碳
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.88,0:00:52.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.37,0:00:57.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.48,0:01:02.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏日的猛兽来势汹汹
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.44,0:01:06.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太狡猾了 面麻也要吃盐拉面
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.02,0:01:10.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 鸡蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.48,0:01:13.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面麻最喜欢鸡蛋汤了 鸡蛋汤
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.58,0:01:22.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸡蛋要凝固了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.58,0:01:27.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把鸡蛋搅拌开 搅拌开 搅拌开
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.62,0:01:28.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么 拉面？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.92,0:01:32.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叔叔 打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.77,0:01:32.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不错嘛 仁太 给我也做一份吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.28,0:01:36.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁太？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.35,0:01:37.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 可以
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.74,0:01:39.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了 真可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.49,0:01:41.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给叔叔做却不给面麻做么
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.05,0:01:43.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说可不可以不要什么都说可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.30,0:01:46.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是这是个好词啊 什么都能套上
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.88,0:01:47.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是叔叔也说面麻很可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.28,0:01:49.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一般都不用吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.20,0:01:50.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸡蛋要什么样的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.16,0:01:52.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来个荷包蛋 不要绞碎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.33,0:01:53.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,OK
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.62,0:01:57.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叔叔也是这样 偏心 偏心 偏心中年人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.51,0:01:59.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.62,0:02:01.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,电视 电视
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.78,0:02:02.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.12,0:02:04.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猫咪好可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.45,0:02:09.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老爸和平时一样 这么看来果然是...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.65,0:02:11.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.29,0:02:13.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做好了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.51,0:02:17.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我开动了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.38,0:02:21.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胡椒 胡椒 胡椒 好了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.48,0:02:26.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面麻也要吃
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.49,0:02:27.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁太？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.82,0:02:29.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.03,0:02:33.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,筷子在哪里 筷子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.63,0:02:33.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.50,0:02:42.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 在家里热得中暑了？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.99,0:02:44.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然可爱 但是糟糕了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.34,0:02:46.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.23,0:02:49.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那时的夏天
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.73,0:02:59.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳 好危险的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.28,0:02:59.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.84,0:03:07.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然 仁碳的这个是最大的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.16,0:03:09.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.01,0:03:12.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的 很厉害 很厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.38,0:03:15.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳真有型
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.45,0:03:17.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那时的我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.67,0:03:19.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鹤见子 什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.64,0:03:21.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 仁碳
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.62,0:03:25.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 面麻
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.61,0:03:30.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.13,0:03:34.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有个愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.80,0:05:21.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.76,0:05:27.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我确实是病了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.34,0:05:30.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这必定是我一直承受的压力
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.33,0:05:33.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与挥之不去的阴影
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.23,0:05:35.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为炎热的夏天而成形
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.62,0:05:40.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甚至协同青春期的性冲动也席卷而来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.67,0:05:49.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好 仁碳
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.17,0:05:56.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就假设你是因为我的压力具现化而出现在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.23,0:06:00.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 为什么到现在才出现
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.37,0:06:06.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且还是以成长后的姿态出现
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.49,0:06:10.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算你这么问我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.67,0:06:13.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.40,0:06:14.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.66,0:06:15.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.92,0:06:19.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概...我想是希望能够实现愿望吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.42,0:06:20.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面麻
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.23,0:06:22.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愿望？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.94,0:06:24.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.38,0:06:26.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恩 那个是...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.36,0:06:29.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.88,0:06:32.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连愿望都不知道是什么 怎么会实现啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.61,0:06:36.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恩 虽然是有点感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.80,0:06:38.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是真的其实是什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.89,0:06:40.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我怎么会知道
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.18,0:06:42.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,口水乱飞啊 真是好讨厌啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.97,0:06:44.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,屏蔽掉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.99,0:06:47.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是夏日的猛兽
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.24,0:06:48.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的压力
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.07,0:06:50.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的阴影
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.65,0:06:51.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.47,0:06:54.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先把那个什么愿望给我想起来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.45,0:06:56.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了对了 那个愿望呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.90,0:06:59.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家不在一起的话就无法实现
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.89,0:07:02.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.19,0:07:04.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.88,0:07:05.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.55,0:07:07.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.26,0:07:09.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 那个 门铃在响
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.20,0:07:11.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要是出现了要怎么办啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.59,0:07:13.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听好了 要乖乖的...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.38,0:07:17.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.84,0:07:21.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鸣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.86,0:07:22.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你冷静一点
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.58,0:07:26.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷静？我并没有在焦急啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.59,0:07:29.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不..没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.88,0:07:32.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉肩膀很重
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.99,0:07:38.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鸣 看不到面麻吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.46,0:07:41.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐 有什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.60,0:07:44.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.91,0:07:48.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师拜托我给你的暑假作业
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.76,0:07:49.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在才给我？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.06,0:07:52.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暑假什么的 只剩下两天了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.64,0:07:56.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和宿海不同 可是很忙的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.18,0:08:00.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然这样的话 随便找个地方扔掉不就好了 这东西
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.22,0:08:03.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正我不会再去那种傻学校了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.14,0:08:06.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宿海来不来无所谓
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.00,0:08:10.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 你太不像样了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.23,0:08:19.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.14,0:08:39.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳你个笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.81,0:08:43.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么没有拜托小鸣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.73,0:08:47.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起来实现愿望吧 小鸣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.81,0:08:49.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事先说明
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.52,0:08:54.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要称她小鸣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.45,0:08:56.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫安城或者鸣子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.70,0:08:59.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么 小鸣就是小鸣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.77,0:09:04.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对大家都很温柔 有好多漫画和游戏
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.22,0:09:05.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都说了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.77,0:09:10.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她已经不是那时的小鸣了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.47,0:09:15.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算去拜托那个臭女人 她也不会帮忙的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.04,0:09:16.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,臭女人？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.75,0:09:18.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是蠢女人的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.36,0:09:20.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之 和她已经不是朋友了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.91,0:09:22.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.07,0:09:28.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要 讨厌说小鸣坏话的仁碳
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.63,0:09:29.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面麻
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.77,0:09:34.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起去小鸣那里 去拜托她吧 仁碳
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.86,0:09:38.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.14,0:09:40.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.63,0:09:44.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所谓的那个愿望说给安城听的话 你会理解的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.96,0:09:51.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不仅是安城 所有的一切都改变了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.75,0:09:59.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳 还没有好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.73,0:10:01.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了来了来了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.54,0:10:08.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帽子和眼镜?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.42,0:10:09.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用在意
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.08,0:10:11.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.32,0:10:12.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.59,0:10:16.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,买东西吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.62,0:10:17.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.47,0:10:18.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.30,0:10:20.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.77,0:10:21.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.92,0:10:32.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.85,0:10:33.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.40,0:10:35.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好怪的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.79,0:10:38.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 脸上有吃拉面的葱的痕迹 Honey
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.73,0:10:39.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啰嗦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.00,0:10:46.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.68,0:10:52.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.45,0:10:58.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鸣的家不在这个方向
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.25,0:11:00.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,顺便散步一下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.71,0:11:06.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里以前是bombom吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.31,0:11:08.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在成了WcDonald了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.44,0:11:11.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害 不过面麻还是更喜欢...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.65,0:11:12.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同校的人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.87,0:11:13.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.15,0:11:15.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是外星人会出来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.79,0:11:18.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有使用双节棍的女人在学校打架的那个
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.76,0:11:19.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.78,0:11:22.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是朋友么？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.52,0:11:26.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.73,0:11:30.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是啊 被大妈破坏了心情
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.12,0:11:33.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁也不会在意我的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.13,0:11:36.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安城也不是说了么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.57,0:11:39.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我这种人无所谓
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.29,0:11:47.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏天的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.66,0:11:50.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还是老样子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.71,0:11:52.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.94,0:11:56.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,理所当然啊 只是幻影而已
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.79,0:12:02.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实现...愿望么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.63,0:12:09.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然这一定是我对面麻的...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.04,0:12:11.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.43,0:12:13.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看 看
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.21,0:12:16.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在做什么 很危险的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.51,0:12:22.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.02,0:12:27.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳 小面麻她...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.41,0:12:46.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁 仁碳
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.19,0:12:50.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不要紧吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.47,0:12:52.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.22,0:12:56.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,疼疼疼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.11,0:13:02.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宿海 你在做什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.06,0:13:07.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第1话 超和平克星
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.57,0:13:18.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 鸣子 你去小仁的家了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.15,0:13:19.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敲门
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.44,0:13:22.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎 我没有吗 算了 还有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.54,0:13:26.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,顺道看了一下而已 这个应该跟妈妈你没关系吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.54,0:13:30.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有啊 我还想让你带点包子去呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.20,0:13:33.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你自己带去不就好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.12,0:13:35.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 青春期 青春期
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.45,0:13:37.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.19,0:13:45.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不像样的是我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.65,0:13:48.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.68,0:13:54.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚从暑假讲习那边回来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.76,0:13:56.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毕竟是新学校
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.93,0:14:00.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我应该穿高中校服的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.53,0:14:02.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.57,0:14:03.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宿海？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.34,0:14:05.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.84,0:14:08.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恩 我先回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.67,0:14:09.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.42,0:14:16.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是雪集和鹤子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.29,0:14:19.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.19,0:14:24.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 不是 是面麻她 呃 不是 是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.07,0:14:26.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你提面麻做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.49,0:14:31.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到现在还在说这话啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.27,0:14:34.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪集？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.87,0:14:35.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我听说了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.70,0:14:36.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪集
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.88,0:14:40.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一直没去上学是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.31,0:14:45.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,考试失败 进入了一个垃圾学校
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.94,0:14:48.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连学校都不去一股劲叫本间芽衣子的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.50,0:14:51.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的大脑是不是坏掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.66,0:14:56.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.92,0:14:59.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪集是大白痴
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.38,0:15:05.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎 你热血什么呀
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.33,0:15:10.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一提到本间芽依子就像换了一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.12,0:15:13.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不也是这样吗 雪集君
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.79,0:15:16.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啰嗦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.32,0:15:20.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是可怜的家伙 只有脸长得帅而已
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.22,0:15:22.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也很聪明的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.90,0:15:23.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.59,0:15:29.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.68,0:15:31.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.85,0:15:35.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.86,0:15:43.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样你总该明白了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.72,0:15:46.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都变了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.96,0:15:52.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 变化最大的应该是我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.87,0:15:54.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳  那个
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.10,0:15:59.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请饶了我的应激反应吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.46,0:16:01.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要有你在
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.20,0:16:05.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就会想起 就会想起不开心的事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.76,0:16:09.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让自己变得急躁起来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.25,0:16:17.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.89,0:16:32.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那时 那时的夏天 不是这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.70,0:16:40.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂 决定了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.25,0:16:42.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.75,0:16:45.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们是超和平克星
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.17,0:16:48.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 太帅了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.18,0:16:50.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克星是？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.78,0:16:52.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貌似是指厉害的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.47,0:16:55.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们要保护和平
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.20,0:16:55.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太帅了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.07,0:16:56.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪里的和平？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.66,0:17:00.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有地方的各种和平
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.84,0:17:04.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么说仁碳是老大
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.22,0:17:06.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.65,0:17:09.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都围绕着我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.13,0:17:16.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 即便那天也是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.32,0:17:21.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 仁碳
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.78,0:17:26.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你喜欢面麻吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.09,0:17:29.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.08,0:17:33.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在说什么呀
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.40,0:17:35.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就诚实的回答吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.49,0:17:38.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们超和平克星是不能有事隐瞒的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.43,0:17:39.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪集
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.59,0:17:42.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说啊 说啊 说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.64,0:17:44.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃 是不行的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.64,0:17:47.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说啊 说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.02,0:17:52.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁 谁会对这丑女
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.67,0:17:58.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我以为她会哭
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.49,0:18:01.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为面麻是哭泣虫
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.87,0:18:03.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.60,0:18:11.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 仁碳
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.51,0:18:13.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.99,0:18:19.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 你回来了呀
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.36,0:18:23.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我先去趟你妈妈那边 把饭热一下再吃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.61,0:18:33.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个笑容深深揪住了我的心
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.46,0:18:37.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原想明天再去道歉好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.76,0:18:39.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真难吃
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.26,0:18:41.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但那个明天
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.03,0:18:45.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永远的都没到来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.76,0:18:58.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咖喱
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.15,0:19:05.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 门开了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.09,0:19:06.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你关掉嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.61,0:19:08.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聪君
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.03,0:19:11.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 长这么大了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.58,0:19:15.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸 满头白发
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.90,0:19:26.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.24,0:19:28.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经够了 你老这么做
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.98,0:19:30.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聪君
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.68,0:19:34.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每次咖喱都要给姐姐一份 看着就难受
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.24,0:19:38.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但这是你姐姐最喜欢吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.04,0:19:41.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死了是不吃东西的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.52,0:19:43.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你别这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.12,0:19:51.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你姐姐缺根筋 说不定还不知自己已经死了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.02,0:19:53.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.65,0:20:00.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面麻对自己已经死掉的事情 还是知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.48,0:20:04.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.11,0:20:06.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我怎么知道 是杯子它自己
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.65,0:20:08.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道是姐姐  （赶快收拾）
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.97,0:20:10.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,切 又不是我做的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.08,0:20:16.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么都什么啊 臭老爸
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.38,0:20:23.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,漂亮的将和平克星除掉的我们
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.00,0:20:29.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无意中都分开了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.81,0:20:42.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面麻最喜欢鸡蛋汤了 鸡蛋汤
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.42,0:20:46.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.52,0:20:55.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 曾经很想要
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.33,0:21:01.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙会去的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.52,0:21:16.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直都很想要那个明天 那个跟面麻道歉的明天
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.20,0:21:24.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面麻
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.10,0:21:29.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的压力
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.22,0:21:33.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的阴影
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.75,0:21:43.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 我一定是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.36,0:21:48.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了向面麻道歉所以制造出了这个面麻
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.00,0:21:51.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以再这样下去的话
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.86,0:22:07.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.87,0:22:17.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.03,0:22:23.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这也太...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.60,0:22:27.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋 正是这种反差才是浪漫吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.08,0:22:31.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 是仁碳啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.20,0:22:33.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,波波
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.65,0:22:37.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我们在这里刻上名字吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.22,0:22:38.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超怎么写？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.97,0:22:40.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.39,0:22:43.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之 左边一个走
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.27,0:22:45.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走怎么写？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.16,0:22:47.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么在这里？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.93,0:22:54.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs25}（超和平Busters）
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.57,0:22:54.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那一天 停止于这里的时间又开始转动
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.94,0:22:59.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面麻应该回哪里才好呢？
